{"tid":1391507,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孫子兵法(一)你班友唔識英文be water點解，孫子用中文教你","createTime":"2019-07-31T12:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T13:20:51.000Z","uid":293677,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7f09a46c199c5e9199a5dfcecc9924eef2fd9096","tid":1391507,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:45:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">兵無常勢，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">水無常形</span></span></strong>，能因敵變化而取勝者，謂之神。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;《孫子兵法&middot;虛實篇》<br />\n<br />\n勢：方式，模式。神：超乎常人的本領。這兩句大意是，用兵作戰<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有固定的模式，就像水沒有固定不變的形態一樣</span></strong>，能根據敵情變化而取勝的，就叫做用兵如神。<br />\n<br />\n孫子認為：戰場上形勢瞬息萬變，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">不能拘泥於某種作戰的形式</span></span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">正像水本無固定的形態一樣，放在圓容器中它就是圓的，放在方容器中它就是方的</span></strong>。能夠根據敵人數量的多少，裝備的好壞，士氣的高低，指揮員素質如何，軍需供應怎樣而機動靈活地採取對策，才能奪取勝利。<br />\n<br />\n這幾句可用以說明用兵或做其他工作應<strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">審時度勢，靈活機動</span></strong></strong>地制訂計劃，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不可死搬教條，墨守成規</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日喺度叫你地be water be water<br />\n係咪唔撚識英文呀<br />\n個個企喺度死守俾狗圍<br />\n俾人當練耙場射到仆街<br />\n係咪要全部手足俾人拉鳩晒先醒呀！"},{"pid":"467c3df58262c88f56f13103563e0d8a550891d4","tid":1391507,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e41c3c8a92e3103217f17357d7d9dbf8f551f3","tid":1391507,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:51:00.000Z","msg":"